OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1771938194
OL,3,CGianluca Prestianni given temporary
OL,4,Cban by UEFA after Vinicius Junior
OL,5,Cincident
OL,7,FBenfica's Gianluca Prestianni has been
OL,8,Fprovisionally suspended for
OL,9,FWednesday's Champions League return
OL,10,Fleg against Real Madrid after he was
OL,11,Faccused of making a racist comment to
OL,12,FVinicius Junior last week.
OL,14,FReal Madrid forward Vinicius alleged
OL,15,Fhe was the subject of racist abuse by
OL,16,Fa Benfica player ` later named by Real
OL,17,Fas Prestianni ` during the first leg
OL,18,Fbetween the clubs last Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
