FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1771938194
OL,3,CGianluca Prestianni given temporary
OL,4,Cban by UEFA after Vinicius Junior
OL,5,Cincident
OL,7,FPrestianni has denied saying anything
OL,8,Fracist to Junior, posting on Instagram
OL,9,Fafter the incident: "I want to clarify
OL,10,Fthat at no point did I direct racist
OL,11,Finsults at the player Vinicius Junior,
OL,12,Fwho unfortunately misinterpreted what
OL,13,Fhe thought he heard."
OL,15,FUEFA on Monday announced a provisional
OL,16,Fone-match ban for Prestianni following
OL,17,Fthe appointment of a UEFA ethics and
OL,18,Fdisciplinary inspector (EDI) to
OL,19,Finvestigate the incident.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
