FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1771938194
OL,3,CGianluca Prestianni given temporary
OL,4,Cban by UEFA after Vinicius Junior
OL,5,Cincident
OL,7,FFurther punishment could be handed out
OL,8,Fonce the investigation is completed,
OL,9,FUEFA said.
OL,11,FIn a statement, UEFA said the
OL,12,Fsuspension was "without prejudice to
OL,13,Fany ruling that the UEFA disciplinary
OL,14,Fbodies may subsequently make".
OL,16,FJunior made the allegation during
OL,17,FReal's 1-0 win in Lisbon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
