PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1771938194
OL,3,CGianluca Prestianni given temporary
OL,4,Cban by UEFA after Vinicius Junior
OL,5,Cincident
OL,7,FThe Brazilian left the field and
OL,8,Frefused to return, resulting in a
OL,9,Fstoppage in play that lasted ten
OL,10,Fminutes.
OL,12,FIt came after Junior had given his
OL,13,Fteam the lead five minutes into the
OL,14,Fsecond half.
OL,16,FAfter celebrating in front of the home
OL,17,Ffans, he became suddenly and visibly
OL,18,Fupset about something said to him and
OL,19,Fimmediately informed the referee, who
OL,20,Fstopped the match.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1771938194
OL,3,CGianluca Prestianni given temporary
OL,4,Cban by UEFA after Vinicius Junior
OL,5,Cincident
OL,7,FAfter Junior returned to the match in
OL,8,Fthe final few minutes of the game,
OL,9,Ffans booed him heavily and threw
OL,10,Fbottles at him.
OL,12,FAt one point, he refused to take a
OL,13,Fcorner because of the abuse from fans.
OL,15,FBenfica boss Jose Mourinho, who was
OL,16,Froundly criticised for his comments
OL,17,Fabout the incident after the game,
OL,18,Fwill not conduct the usual pre-match
OL,19,Fpress conference on Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
