FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1771938194
OL,3,CGianluca Prestianni given temporary
OL,4,Cban by UEFA after Vinicius Junior
OL,5,Cincident
OL,7,FMourinho appeared to say that the
OL,8,Fwinger had brought any abuse upon
OL,9,Fhimself with his celebration, and said
OL,10,Fthat "a stadium where Vinicius plays,
OL,11,Fsomething happens, always."
OL,13,FAnti-discriminatory organisation Kick
OL,14,FIt Out responded by accusing Mourinho
OL,15,Fof "gaslighting".
OL,17,FBenfica announced on Monday that
OL,18,Fassistant coach Joao Tralhao will
OL,19,Fundertake media duties at the
OL,20,FBernabeu, with no explanation given
OL,21,Ffor Mourinho's absence.
